.TH smi-start-diskless "1" "October 2025" "SMI Toolset 0.100.0" "SMI Diskless Command"
.SH NAME
smi-start-diskless \- Restart all diskless-related servers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B smi-start-diskless
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
.B smi-start-diskless
restarts the host services required for diskless clients to boot and run.
Specifically, it restarts:
.IP 1.
\fBdhcp-server\fR
.IP 2.
\fBtftp\fR (Systemd socket/service)
.IP 3.
\fBnfs-server\fR
.SH AUTHOR
.PP
Command written by Imre Tabur.
Documentation written by Imre Tabur.
